sensorsdata.portal.v2.Statement.description:
权限描述结构定义，参考下面几个示例：
 ```
 允许 operation code=8013 的操作：{"operation": "8013", "effect": "ALLOW"}
 禁用 operation code=8013 的操作：{"operation": "8013", "effect": "DENY"}
 允许对资源 id 为 [4，5] 的资源执行 operation code = 8013 的操作：
 {
   "operation": "8013",
   "effect": "ALLOW",
   "condition": {
     "operator": "OR",
     "conditions": [
       {
         "function": "EQUAL",
         "params": [
           {
             "param_type": "FIELD",
             "field": "#ResourceId",
             "variable": "",
             "expression": "",
             "value": {"list_value": ["4","5"]}
           }
         ]
       }
     ]
   }
 }
 ```
